name: AskAnkeny
0:
”Alexa, open Ankeny Info.”
”What are the hours for the library?”
”Alexa, ask Ankeny Info for the phone number for city hall”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ankeny info
des: Ask Ankeny provides hours and phone numbers for many of of the City of Ankeny services, including Kirkendall Public Library, city hall, police, fire and more.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
